> # 道路 一定会衍生出: 途径，关系，方法，手段等含义，大道至简！
> # r n h
period   n.时期;学时;句号
> late Middle English (denoting the time during which something, especially a disease, runs its course): from Old French periode, via Latin from Greek periodos 'orbit, recurrence, course', from peri- 'around' + hodos 'way, course'. The sense 'portion of time' dates from the early 17th cent

> per 由此到彼 一直； peri=around 围绕 周围
> od = hod = hood 覆盖 途径 关系 方法
> -hood 后缀，表名词,多加在名词后,"时期,性质"等
> road n. 路; 通路; 途径; 方法;
> way 道路 方法 方向(面)

periodical   n.期刊，杂志
periodic     n.周期的;一定时期的

method   n.方法，办法;教学法
> late Middle English (in the sense 'prescribed medical treatment for a disease'): via Latin from Greek methodos 'pursuit of knowledge', from meta- (expressing development) + hodos 'way'

hodometer   n.车程计; 里程计;
methodical   a.有方法的,有系统的
